{
  "stem": "3382.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we worked there, you know, in the military barracks building, rebuilding various things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was-- when the commander of the Einsatzgruppen, who was there-- so it was all the time, terrible beatings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They beat for anything, what-- you didn't stand properly, you were hit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't run too fast, you were hit, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I'm not yet in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is summer-- it was in August, through August.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- and then, it started to rumor that they'll organize ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember I argued with her brother-- with Rachela's brother, what will be better, to be all together in the ghetto or be separated?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, I was called once to-- for work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I say called for work, despite the [NON-ENGLISH], the commander, rather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And once I was unloading some kind of food for Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but once, they took us to [NON-ENGLISH], where there was a company of those SS men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we came up to this place-- to the very first thing that I saw-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] several graves, fresh graves, you know-- scent.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So what they did, you know, they made out of us chain and were driving us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they saw-- they suspected that there might be mines.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because before the-- before they came there, were these sort of garrisons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They suspect there are-- so instead of looking for mines themselves, they, you know, make a human chain and tried to do it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and I remember Zelig, telling me, this is our last day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I told him, look, there are two possibilities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I have a watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'll give the [NON-ENGLISH], the German-- I'll grab the watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'll start a run to-- through the forest, the respite.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
